# Copy to .env and fill in to enable decryption of encrypted TeslaCam clips (firmware 2026.20+).
# Obtain a refresh token once with the tesla-dashcam-decrypt tool (auth.py login), which mints a
# token with scope=offline_access on client_id=dashcam. It rotates automatically after that.
#
# Alternatively, paste a short-lived access token (from dashcam.tesla.com DevTools) via
# TESLA_ACCESS_TOKEN — it works until it expires (~8h) with no auto-refresh.
TESLA_REFRESH_TOKEN=
# TESLA_ACCESS_TOKEN=
